Steps.Message: Update at 02:23 - We're very sorry we've had to switch off your electricity. Our engineers have turned off the power in the TN14 7, BR6 7 area in the interest of the public's health and safety. This is so they can investigate reports of an overhead cable coming down. The estimated time to have you back on is between 03:00 and 04:00 We'll keep you updated with our progress.

We became aware of this power cut at 02:07. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically
